Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:24.14,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,你嘟着嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:31.03,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,表情里看出了小九九
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:36.32,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,因为那份若即若离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:46.25,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,被你藏到了口袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:53.17,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,回忆是黑白照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:58.39,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,为它添上颜色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:06.94,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,再一次来到我的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:12.15,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,我五彩斑斓的宝贝女儿
